{
  "stem": "18670.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[YIDDISH] When I said, no, which we didn't, between the brother-- my brother and I, we had a little over $10.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He said [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he didn't believe us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we walked out Hoboken, up stairs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was going to get a taxi to take us to where he lived in New York, in Manhattan.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was called Harlem.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He stopped at the first taxi and he was bargaining with the guy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was a very warm day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The sun was out and we were wearing winter clothing and schlepping two suitcases.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we walked-- each taxi parked there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was bargaining with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he-- they all gave him the same price, from $1.50 to $1.25.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Finally, at the end of the block-- he was not a young man-- he took the taxi.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We arrived in Harlem.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He said, pay the man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I knew he wouldn't part with $10.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I know already what I'm up against.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He still hadn't asked my mother is, or how my father is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And-- but he was religious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Then we got up to the apartment and the doorbell was ringing and there's somebody delivering his shirts and he asked me to pay the guy with the shirts.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I said, I have no money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that was my first experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I arrived on a Friday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "On Saturday, you don't go looking for a job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "On Sunday, you don't look for a job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I found out there's such a thing as the Garment District down on University Place, 14th Street.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "On Monday morning, I walked down to 14th Street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I didn't want to spend any money on the subway, because God knows how long this $10 and change has to last.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
